665
01:20:21,662 --> 01:20:22,661
Brooke?

666
01:20:23,163 --> 01:20:24,162
Brooky!

667
01:20:25,497 --> 01:20:26,496
Brooke!

668
01:20:27,396 --> 01:20:28,395
